        "timestamp": "2017-09-11 17:40:04.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1\n\n(2 comments)\n\nGlobal: This code is executed quite frequently.  Here is how you should treat the log statements:\n - Convert all statements to use the {} parameter insertion format.  This also includes all that have a string msg built before being inserted into the logger statement.\n - Surround all logger.debug statements with a block: if(logger.isDebugEnabled{...}\n - Convert all logger.info statements to logger.debug and surround with isDebugEnabled block.\n\nThis applies to all the classes except the test class.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
